ay's forecast: Clear skies, breezy weather and cooltemperatures are forecast for Iraq. Later today clouds will increase and therewill be stray showers over parts of Israel, northern Saudi Arabia, Iraq,Kuwait and most of Iran.; Temperatures:;  Today  Tomorrow;  Hi Lo    Hi  Lo;Amman  54 38  54  36; Baghdad  54 38  56  36; Damascus  51 37  51  35; Dhahran 72 52  76  52; Riyadh  68 48  72  48  </TEXT><COUNTRY>  USA  </COUNTRY><EDITION>  Morning Final  </EDITION><CODE>  SJ  </CODE><NAME>  SAN JOSE MERCURY NEWS  </NAME><PUBDATE>   910218  </PUBDATE> <DAY>  Monday  </DAY><MONTH>  February  </MONTH><PG.COL>  16A  </PG.COL><PUBYEAR>  1991  </PUBYEAR><REGION>  WEST  </REGION><STATE>  CA  </STATE><WORD.CT>  342  </WORD.CT><DATELINE>  Monday February 18, 199100049101,SJ1  </DATELINE><COPYRGHT>  Copyright 1991, San Jose Mercury News  </COPYRGHT><LIMLEN>  1  </LIMLEN><LANGUAGE>  ENG  </LANGUAGE></DOC>